# .env.example — template for your environment configuration
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
#   1. Copy this file:   cp .env.example .env
#   2. Open .env and replace 'paste-your-key-here' with your OpenRouter API key
#   3. Never commit your .env file — it contains a secret key
#      (it's already listed in .gitignore, so git will ignore it automatically)
#
# WHY A .env FILE?
#   Hardcoding an API key in your source code is dangerous — anyone who reads
#   your code (or your git history) would have your key. The .env file keeps
#   secrets separate from code, and .gitignore keeps it off GitHub.

OPENROUTER_API_KEY=paste-your-key-here
